ciency and Cost Savings with Table Lamps<\/h2>\n    <p>Table lamps are stylish and cost-effective, using less electricity than main lights, especially with LED bulbs.<\/p>\n    <p>At Ledsone, our <strong>energy-efficient industrial<\/strong> and <strong>modern table lamps<\/strong> deliver great illumination while keeping energy bills low.<\/p>\n    <p>LED bulbs used in table lamps are more energy-efficient and longer-lasting than traditional bulbs. For example:<\/p>\n\n    <ul>\n        <li><strong>Touch table lamps:<\/strong> Offer convenience and energy savings.<\/li>\n        <li>Models with timers or smart controls ensure you don’t waste electricity by leaving them on needlessly.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <p>When used strategically, table lamps can significantly reduce your household energy consumption.<\/p>\n\n    <hr>\n\n    <h2>Enhancing Every Room with Table Lamps<\/h2>\n    <p>Table lamps are incredibly versatile and can enhance any room in your home:<\/p>\n\n    <ul>\n        <li><strong>Living Rooms:<\/strong> Combine <strong>table lamps and floor lamps<\/strong> for layered lighting that creates a cozy ambiance. Use <strong>contemporary table lamps<\/strong> to highlight decor elements or reading corners.<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Bedrooms:<\/strong> Opt for <strong>modern bedroom side table lamps<\/strong> or <strong>contemporary night table lamps<\/strong> to add functionality and warmth.<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Hallways:<\/strong> Add a welcoming touch with <strong>table lamps for a hallway<\/strong> or a <strong>console table lamp<\/strong> placed on an entryway table.<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Workspaces:<\/strong> Pick <strong>industrial table lamps<\/strong> for bright lighting. They help you focus and add style to your desk or study area.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"gallery_aFQW4d":{"type":"gallery","blocks":{"image_renDfq":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/PLTYBC_WCBNBC_ICST64E2740.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-table-lamp"}},"image_dmxDrd":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Modern_Ceramic_Base_Table_Lamp_28df827e-e6e2-4419-9c9e-02f71cd0e9f2.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-table-lamp"}},"image_9bg8Bz":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/09_5_2a33c0c7-ce8a-4f45-929c-8f44f249fb4d.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/desk-lamp-wood-bedside-table-lamp-plugin-light"}},"image_A4MV6U":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/o_dUWfHrN2eb.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/colorful-mosaic-lamp-for-uk"}}},"block_order":["image_renDfq","image_dmxDrd","image_9bg8Bz","image_A4MV6U"],"settings":{"heading":"Transform Your Space with Beautiful Table Lamps","description":"","text_align":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","layout_type":"carousel","column_gap":30,"aspect_ratio":"original","custom_ratio":"21:9","actions_click":"unset","custom_column":3,"grid_image_desktop":4,"autoplay":false,"loop":false,"show_arrow":false,"show_bullet":true,"show_bullet_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_liquid_CAHxTN":{"type":"custom-liquid","settings":{"heading":"","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","content_liquid":"<h2>Why Choose Ledsone for Your Table Lamp Needs?<\/h2>\n    <p>At Ledsone, we offer a wide range of high-quality table lamps to suit every need and style.<\/p>\n    <p>We design our lamps with energy efficiency in mind, ensuring you enjoy both style and functionality.<\/p>\n    <p>With competitive prices, durable materials, and timeless designs, Ledsone is your trusted source for table lamps and lighting solutions.<\/p>\n\n    <hr>\n\n    <h2>Conclusion<\/h2>\n    <p>Table lamps are a must-have for any home. They bring light, style, and character to your spaces while offering practical benefits like energy efficiency.<\/p>\n    <p>Whether furnishing a bedroom, decorating a living room, or enhancing a hallway, Ledsone has the perfect table lamp for you.<\/p>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"faq_j4pm6T":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"faq_7kLypm":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"How big should a lamp be over a table?","content":"<p>A table lamp should be proportional to the table it sits on. The lamp should be about 1.5 times the height of the table, with the lampshade at eye level for optimal lighting and comfort.<\/p>"}},"faq_J3YAhD":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Are table lamps still in style?","content":"<p>Yes, table lamps remain timeless and versatile. Trendy styles like industrial, modern, and brass table lamps suit various design aesthetics.<\/p>"}},"faq_r4a7H7":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Do table lamps use less electricity?","content":"<p>Yes, table lamps consume less electricity than overhead lights, especially when fitted with LED bulbs.<\/p>"}},"faq_pwLcLP":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Is it cheaper to run a lamp or a main light?","content":"<p>Running a table lamp is generally cheaper than a main light. For added savings, choose energy-efficient options like LED touch table lamps.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_7kLypm","faq_J3YAhD","faq_r4a7H7","faq_pwLcLP"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}}},"order":["main-collection-heading","8498460c-0376-40d1-bafc-199edbe0edfc","439e38df-206c-40a8-9cd5-fc0e5f00f9d3","product-grid","b1a1633c-9de0-43c8-8a60-a0eddc69dfb1","47b4aaae-a5a7-401b-a79c-d7b0652caf69","divider_PhNww8","custom_text_qedYj9","banner_image_bUhTqD","custom_liquid_BPkHwA","gallery_rdw6wK","custom_liquid_NKDQi4","gallery_aFQW4d","custom_liquid_CAHxTN","faq_j4pm6T"]}